OL,5,Cvehicle
OL,7,FA jury has found a father who hit his
OL,8,Fthree-year-old son with a farm vehicle
OL,9,Fhas been cleared of gross negligence
OL,10,Fmanslaughter.
OL,12,FNeil Speakman was charged after he
OL,13,Freversed his telehandler, a multi-
OL,14,Fpurpose farm vehicle, into his son
OL,15,FAlbie on his farm in Bury on 16 July
OL,16,F2022.
