OL,7,FManchester Minshull Street Court heard
OL,8,Fthat Albie was struck in the garden
OL,9,Fwhile he played with the family's
OL,10,Fdogs, and was left with catastrophic
OL,11,Fhead injuries. He died in hospital
OL,12,Fsome hours later.
OL,14,FGiving evidence at his trial, Neil
OL,15,Fsaid: "I shouldn't have to do this,
OL,16,Fit's f*****g not fair.
