OL,5,Cvehicle
OL,7,FHe said it was "second nature" to
OL,8,Fexaggerate looking as there was no
OL,9,Fmirror, so he would "profusely check
OL,10,Fthe blind spots".
OL,12,FHe said: "They need to know that I
OL,13,Flooked to see if he was there, I knew
OL,14,Fto look for him, I knew to look for my
OL,15,Flittle boy.
OL,17,F"I'm careful with him, I'm always
OL,18,Fcareful in what I do. He was my little
OL,19,Fboy," he said, breaking down in tears.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
