OL,7,FAsked if he saw Albie, he said: "No, I
OL,8,Ffelt a bump, instantly. It felt like a
OL,9,Fhouse brick, I'd only gone back 10 or
OL,10,F20 centimetres. I felt a bump and
OL,11,Fthought s***t, what's that?
OL,13,FFollowing a break, Mr Speakman added:
OL,14,F"I jumped off the machine, I rushed
OL,15,Fround and I scooped him up in my arms
OL,16,Fbut there was no response."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
