OL,7,FHe said he ran into the farmhouse and
OL,8,Ftried to perform CPR while a 999 call
OL,9,Fwas made. Mr Speakman said was a
OL,10,F'blur' from that point to taking Albie
OL,11,Fto hospital.
OL,13,FWhile Speakman had used the Kramer
OL,14,Ftelehandler before, he was not
OL,15,Fofficially trained, his trial heard.
OL,16,FThe machine had various defects,
OL,17,Fincluding a missing wing mirror.
