OL,7,FThe prosecution told jurors at the
OL,8,FMinshull Street Crown Court trial
OL,9,FAlbie died "as a result of his
OL,10,Ffather's negligence, which created a
OL,11,Fserious and obvious risk of death".
OL,13,FIn cross examination, Mr Elvidge asked
OL,14,Fwhat Mr Speakman did to keep Albie
OL,15,Fsafe while he played outside. He
OL,16,Freplied: "I checked and checked again
OL,17,Fto make sure he wasn't."
OL,19,F"Why didn't you put him inside?," the
OL,20,Fprosecutor asked.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
