OL,4,Chitting three-year-old son with farm
OL,5,Cvehicle
OL,7,F"He was three-years-old, it was 32
OL,8,Fdegrees, he wanted to play outside
OL,9,Fwith the dogs," Mr Speakman said.
OL,11,F"Do you want me to lock him in the
OL,12,Fhouse? Is that the world you live in?
OL,13,FWhy would I risk my son's f******
OL,14,Fsafety?."
OL,16,FMr Elvidge then referred back to his
OL,17,Fpolice interview, in which he told
OL,18,Fofficers: "He (Albie) knew, he weren't
OL,19,Ff****** stupid stupid. It's a farm
OL,20,Fisn't it? not a f****** playground and
OL,21,Fhe knows that.
OL,26,@zD@OpmzD@Upn
