OL,7,F"He knows boundaries, he knows where
OL,8,Fto go and where not to go and what to
OL,9,Fgo near and what not to go f******
OL,10,Fnear."
OL,12,FThe prosecutor said: "He was three.
OL,13,FAre you suggesting that he was
OL,14,Fresponsible for managing his own risk?"
