OL,7,FThe telehandler was later inspected by
OL,8,Fhealth and safety inspectors and found
OL,9,Fits various defects would have
OL,10,Fhindered safe operation. It concluded
OL,11,Fit was 'foreseeable that persons in
OL,12,Fthe vicinity of the vehicle could be
OL,13,Finjured or killed when the vehicle was
OL,14,Fworking'.
OL,16,FBut on Tuesday 4 February, jurors
OL,17,Ffound Speakman not guilty, clearing
OL,18,Fhim of gross negligence manslaughter.
